      "$description": "Editorial voice — used for the display heading at 68px, all body copy at 20px, card titles, and supporting paragraphs. The serif carries personality; its presence in body text (unusual for tech sites) signals research-publication DNA. Weight 400 is default, 600 for emphasis."
